name: the secret of stratovolcano
description:
A few months ago I decided to move house from Jakarta to Garut, and settled here with my wife.

In Garut, the air is cooler, the sky is blue and there is minimal pollution, very different from the city of Jakarta.

My house is very close to Mount Guntur, the most active volcano in Java.

Mount Guntur is very beautiful when viewed from my house, but has many Mystical Stories, Many Tales of Hikers who mysteriously disappeared in this Mountain. But the climber who disappeared for a few days was safe and healthy after being found.

this is a continuation of the series
'Lost in the dark'
